          <h2>A Legacy of Commercial &amp; Industrial Firsts</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="about-body reveal delay-1">
          <p>Commercially, the Company is known to have established the first warehouse dedicated solely to Saudi Aramco — supplying Aramco's first locally purchased order for steel pipes, tugboats, and tires.</p>
          <p>Industrially, the Company pioneered a soft-drinks bottling factory in the mid-1950s and co-founded the first electric power station and Saudi cement plant in the Eastern Province of the Kingdom.</p>
          <p>Over the decades, the enterprise has grown into successful businesses spanning manufacturing, trading, shipping, real estate, agriculture, travel services, media, and hospitality — with branches throughout the Kingdom.</p>
          <p>Social and environmental responsibilities have remained central to the Company's strategy — reflected in its support for community welfare societies and charitable contributions in Saudi Arabia and abroad.</p>
        </div>
